{
  "stem": "4670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw that they had certainly been in a skirmish because there were damage, not on the outside, on the inside, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took me down, then he took me out again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we sat in front of the ship and he said to me, well, now that I showed you, you have to give me a-- you've got to go out on a date with me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it hit me, all of a sudden, what I had done.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was stupid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he said, what your name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I gave him a name, anything that popped in my head that was a German name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he asked me where I lived, and I gave him a fictitious address.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about Bremerhaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said I'd meet him the next day for lunch, and he loved that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I quickly ran back to my aunt and uncle, and it dawned on me what I had done.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had endangered my whole family, because if that had come out, a Jewish girl with a sailor on a ship that had been-- and that ship had been on a skirmish-- I think it was a skirmish that they had provoked in Spain, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went in to my aunt and uncle's place and they said to me-- you know, asked me-- and I didn't tell him what happened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the next day, their apartment was right next to the store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was like a hallway in between.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my aunt asked me to bring my uncle some coffee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had this tray, and I was just going to open the door of the store, and there was a sailor looking into the case.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
